Register with the new merckmedco.com today and your next prescription order

can be even easier.


Registering with merckmedco.com gives you access to personal, relevant

information and services - tailored just for you! Registration is a one-time

process that must be completed to access merckmedco.com's new features ---

none

of which are available through our standard online offering. Registration also

saves you time each time you return to the site. Once you are registered, all

you

need to do is log in using the e-mail address and password you created during

registration.


To register with merckmedco.com:

* Simply follow this link: http://www.merckmedco.com

* Click on the blue "Click here to register" button.

* Follow the easy steps outlined to complete registration.

Be sure to have your member number and a prescription (Rx) number handy for

registration. Remember, you will only need to enter this information once and

you are on your way!


Once you are registered, you can enjoy:

* simple add-to-cart ordering for prescription refills and renewals;

* more prescription information than ever before;

* 12 months of detailed prescription history;

* coverage and pricing for brand-name and generic medication comparisons at

  both mail and retail;

* the opportunity to take advantage of mail service savings;

* personalized health topics based on your expressed interests;

* ... and much more!


Register with us online at http://www.merckmedco.com and start enjoying our

enhanced features today!


merckmedco.com does not accept e-mail responses directly to this e-mail

address. To help ensure the highest levels of service, we ask that you

direct all inquiries to our web site's Customer Service area by using

the link above or by calling your toll-free Member Services phone number.


